{"id": 904, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在什么时候会觉得“啊！我已经尽力了”？", "description": "外卖优惠券满三百减二百……（题图来自：Nicolas Dehghani）", "record_count": 5533, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183707gUdEcoKjW5pyPDCJ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-03T01:01:16Z", "options": [{"id": 63745, "content": "减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508296}, {"id": 64002, "content": "吃饭实在塞不进去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162214}, {"id": 63492, "content": "劝人的时候吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546634}, {"id": 63748, "content": "考试的时候…", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547950}, {"id": 64004, "content": "追你追得差一点要放弃自己了，对不起，我爱你，但是我有义务成为自己喜欢的人，而不是你喜欢的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 96360}, {"id": 63493, "content": "练一字马到实在不去的时候时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 513773}, {"id": 63749, "content": "减肥，每天晚餐只喝酸奶吃黄瓜，可还是吃了一顿火锅。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182632bRHPyDIikwqEC6So.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547939}, {"id": 63494, "content": "看高考成绩的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468794}, {"id": 63750, "content": "早上起床扣内衣扣子", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547954}, {"id": 64006, "content": "解数学题时", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 549198}, {"id": 63495, "content": "考完试 看到同学对答案 这样宽慰自己", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161701n8BFQgT2lAz1Z4XD.jpg", "praise_count": 113, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239957}, {"id": 63751, "content": "在做自己不想做，却又不得不做的事情时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547966}, {"id": 63496, "content": "工作的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546680}, {"id": 63752, "content": "和一个大傻子讲理，但又不得不和他说的时候！艹", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43694}, {"id": 64008, "content": "起床起不来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539945}, {"id": 63497, "content": "满二十起送减十 我买了十九", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535587}, {"id": 64009, "content": "认真做完一个作品但得分却和抄袭作业的同学得分一个层次，甚至还低。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403368}, {"id": 63498, "content": "deadline前", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139545}, {"id": 63754, "content": "放弃一个暗恋很久的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545556}, {"id": 63499, "content": "被傻逼劝", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531264}, {"id": 63755, "content": "追了很多年的女生从来没有成功过，决定从此放弃的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232346}, {"id": 63500, "content": "推杠铃到一半的时候，上不去了，挺不住了", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536817}, {"id": 64012, "content": "想回家", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 549351}, {"id": 63501, "content": "努力在公司饭局上为老板的笑话笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 104025}, {"id": 63757, "content": "没有尽力的时候。。。。", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161510OUoVcGYdHX2QCjiu.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462954}, {"id": 64269, "content": "早晨赖床迟到……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 210238}, {"id": 63502, "content": "听一个心机婊卖蠢，听到后来扭头就走了我真的是尽力了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 59914}, {"id": 63758, "content": "没有尽力的时候。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462954}, {"id": 63503, "content": "录取了", "image": null, "praise_